<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 21:13:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着美国总统竞选结束，从台湾到贸易，中国准备迎接更多竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-trade-china-braces-more-rivalry-close-us-presidential-race-ends-2024-11-05/</link><description>随着美国人在数十年来最激烈的总统选举之一中进行投票，中国做好了准备，无论谁获胜，都将导致超级大国在贸易、技术和安全问题上的激烈竞争再持续四年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 17:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-trade-china-braces-more-rivalry-close-us-presidential-race-ends-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康股价因潜在的中国调查影响而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-shares-fall-report-potential-china-probe-fallout-2024-11-05/</link><description>阿斯利康股价周二录得自 2020 年 3 月以来最糟糕的一天，此前有报道称，该制药商在中国的数十名高管可能卷入中国制药行业多年来最大的保险欺诈案。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 16:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-shares-fall-report-potential-china-probe-fallout-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>共和党议员称美国需要打击中国芯片制造商中芯国际</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-needs-crack-down-chinese-chipmaker-smic-republican-lawmaker-says-2024-11-05/</link><description>一位共和党高级议员指责拜登政府没有采取足够措施阻止中国半导体制造国际公司（中芯国际）加强该国的芯片制造行业和军工联合体。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 15:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-needs-crack-down-chinese-chipmaker-smic-republican-lawmaker-says-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>科比终结光州完美开局亚冠登顶</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kobe-end-gwangjus-perfect-start-go-top-asian-champions-league-2024-11-05/</link><description>日本神户胜利船周二在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛东区积分榜上跃居榜首，J联赛冠军光州FC以2-0战胜神户，结束了联赛阶段的完美开局。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 14:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kobe-end-gwangjus-perfect-start-go-top-asian-champions-league-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>文件显示，中国希望在COP29气候峰会上就贸易措施进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-wants-talks-trade-measures-cop29-climate-summit-document-shows-2024-11-05/</link><description>路透社看到的一份文件显示，中国已要求各国在下周举行的 COP29 联合国气候峰会上就碳边境税和其他“限制性贸易措施”举行会谈，北京称这些措施正在伤害发展中国家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 13:59:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-wants-talks-trade-measures-cop29-climate-summit-document-shows-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>小米投诉后印度召回 Flipkart 反垄断调查报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-recalls-flipkart-antitrust-probe-report-after-xiaomi-complaint-2024-11-05/</link><description>一份文件显示，印度反垄断机构已召回其对电子商务巨头沃尔玛旗下 Flipkart 违反竞争法的调查报告，这是继 8 月份针对苹果的报告被撤销后的第二次此类举措。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 13:55:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-recalls-flipkart-antitrust-probe-report-after-xiaomi-complaint-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>Shein 和 Temu 为 2026 年英国版权和竞争索赔审判做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-temu-gear-up-2026-uk-trial-over-copyright-competition-claims-2024-11-05/</link><description>在线快时尚平台 Shein 和 Temu 正准备于 2026 年在伦敦高等法院接受审判，竞争对手在相互竞争的诉讼中相互指控侵犯版权和反竞争行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 12:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-temu-gear-up-2026-uk-trial-over-copyright-competition-claims-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：美国决定，世界市场坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-11-05/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 11:11:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国媒体报道，中石化天然气公司前高管因受贿被判入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-sinopec-gas-executive-gets-jail-time-taking-bribes-chinese-media-reports-2024-11-05/</link><description>据中国半官方通讯社中新社周二报道，中国石化一名前高管因受贿被判处 14 年有期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 08:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-sinopec-gas-executive-gets-jail-time-taking-bribes-chinese-media-reports-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾部长称北约式东南亚安全组织不可行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nato-type-southeast-asian-security-group-not-feasible-philippines-minister-says-2024-11-05/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周二表示，鉴于该地区的利益和联盟存在分歧，目前不可能在东南亚建立类似于北大西洋公约组织（北约）的安全组织。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 08:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nato-type-southeast-asian-security-group-not-feasible-philippines-minister-says-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国对更多婴儿的最新呼声可能会被置若罔闻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-cry-more-babies-may-fall-deaf-ears-2024-11-05/</link><description>人口统计学家表示，上周制定的政策对法国和瑞典等国家很有帮助，但在东亚却没有起到作用，很可能是由于性别不平等程度较高。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 08:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-cry-more-babies-may-fall-deaf-ears-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>施罗德因大额客户退出而受到打击，股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/schroders-quarterly-flows-hit-by-china-market-volatility-2024-11-05/</link><description>施罗德周二报告称，第三季度资金流出逊于预期，而且即将失去更多大客户委托，这一令人沮丧的最新消息导致该公司股价在新任首席执行官理查德·奥德菲尔德(Richard Oldfield)上任几天前暴跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 07:31:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/schroders-quarterly-flows-hit-by-china-market-volatility-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国与欧洲混乱的电动汽车争端使贸易紧张局势得到控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-messy-ev-dispute-with-europe-keeps-trade-tensions-check-2024-11-05/</link><description>尽管电动汽车贸易谈判陷入僵局，但对中国与其他主要出口国之间关税战扩大的担忧使得世界第二大经济体与欧盟之间的外交保持活力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 06:58:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-messy-ev-dispute-with-europe-keeps-trade-tensions-check-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦发生枪击事件 两名中国公民受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-chinese-nationals-injured-after-being-shot-pakistans-karachi-authorities-say-2024-11-05/</link><description>周二，一名私人保安向巴基斯坦商业中心卡拉奇的一家服装厂开枪，造成两名中国公民受伤，这是一系列袭击事件中的最新一起，促使北京向伊斯兰堡施压，要求其改善公民的安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 06:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-chinese-nationals-injured-after-being-shot-pakistans-karachi-authorities-say-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲第三季度财报半期：投资者奖励好消息，但对中国感到担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/q3-half-time-europe-investors-reward-beats-fret-about-china-2024-11-05/</link><description>欧洲第三季度盈利大多超出了市场的低预期，投资者的回报比多年来更加丰厚，尽管中国需求疲软令人谨慎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 06:15:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/q3-half-time-europe-investors-reward-beats-fret-about-china-2024-11-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>